title: Titans left tackle Taylor Lewan not in a talkative mood on Thursday
text:
Titans left tackle Taylor Lewan not in a talkative mood on Thursday 
Updated: Thu, Oct 15 2015, 06:30 PM 
Stream WZTV Fox 17 Newscasts LIVE starting with Fox 17 This Morning at 4:30am, News at 5:30pm and News at 9pm & 10 pm 

Taylor Lewan didn't feel like answering questions from reporters on Thursday. Instead, the Titans left tackle telling us to direct all questions to fellow offensive lineman Andy Gallik. 
FOX 17 Sports Director Paul Jones took the hint...quite literally as you'll see in this video.
